# secret-santa
Secret Santa is a Western Christmas tradition in which members of a group or community are randomly assigned a person to whom they anonymously give a gift.
Workflow:
Every person take their email adress via web page.
When all emails recieved, we can start the assigment process: emails mixing and then every gifter get email message with their pair.

Written to try out Clojure Ring and Compojure libraries.

Distributed under the Eclipse Public License, the same as Clojure.
